ConnectBeez Privacy Policy

1. Introduction

Welcome to the ConnectBeez Privacy Policy. This policy describes how Gohetrix we collects, uses, and shares personal information when you use our ConnectBeez mobile application. By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect

Information You Provide: We collect information you provide when you register an account, fill out forms, or communicate with us.
Automatically Collected Information: We may automatically collect certain information about your device, including device information, log information, and location information.
3. How We Use Your Information

We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including to provide and maintain the App, personalize your experience, communicate with you, and analyze usage to improve the App.

4. Data Sharing

We do not share personal information with third parties except as described in this Privacy Policy or with your consent.

5. Data Retention

We retain personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, or until the user requests its deletion.

6. Your Choices

You may choose to opt-out of certain data collection and sharing. However, opting out may limit your ability to use certain features of the App.

7. Security

ConnectBeez employs measures such as email verification to help ensure the security of users' personal information.

8. Children's Privacy

ConnectBeez is intended for users aged 16 and older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 16. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.

9. Changes to This Privacy Policy

In the event that updates or changes to the app result in a violation of the terms and conditions, ConnectBeez will promptly update the privacy policy to reflect any necessary modifications. Users will be notified of any material changes to the privacy policy via the app or other appropriate means.

10. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at connectbeezofficial@gmail.com.
